      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just a note for future evolution of this stuff: As we go forward with adding more stats using the macros that hook into UMA perhaps we should also look at unifying the implementation with the GPU stats that we pump into perf.skia.org (even if we don\u0027t make Chrome UMA metrics out of all of the collected values).",
